sandra.libs.nlu.nlulib
Class SemanticParsing

java.lang.Object
  sandra.libs.nlu.nlulib.SemanticParsing

 class SemanticParsing
extends java.lang.Object

Represents the semantic parsing for a phrase, including the position index that allows to determine the group of the regular expression that should match the text that triggers each tag.

1.0, 08/23/13
